Name: Fatrifice
About the game: In order to summon a demon, one girl must stuff herself to be the ultimate fatrifice! Help her expand into new shapes and sizes by feeding her! FEATURES A cute girl who gains weight. A fun and lovable story. Timed-clicking minigame. Gallery to revisit your favorite moments. Normal and hard difficulties. 2 endings. Censored and uncensored options.
